The Chronicle Sikhumbuzo Moyo, Senior Sports Reporter TANZANIAN based former Highlanders utility player Bruce Kangwa has predicted a win for the Bulawayo giants when they collide with Caps United in a blockbuster encounter at Barbourfields Stadium this Sunday. Now turning out for Azam in the Tanzanian top league, Kangwa predicted a 1-0 win for Amahlolanyama over a buoyant Green Machine who got off to a flying start in the 2019 Castle Lager Premier Soccer League when they registered a 2-0 win over expensively assembled league debutants Manica Diamonds while Bosso choked a one all draw against bogey side Black Rhinos. Both matches were played at the National Sports Stadiu. More to followâ€¦